			                        <p>Solidify the core of your business by polishing the fundamental attributes of your ogranization.</p>
			                    </figcaption>           
			                </figure>
			                <figure class="effect-slidedown one-half">
			                    <img src="/wt_office_hunddle/static/src/images/2marketing.png" alt="img02"/>
