			                        <img src="/wt_office_hunddle/static/src/images/5leadgen.png" alt="img02"/>
			                        <figcaption class="gray">
			                            <p>Increase the number of opportunities in lead mining by knowing and applying effective methods in the game play of sourcing for potential clients, at the right place, and time.</p>
			                        </figcaption>           
