			                                <p>Make full use of the generated leads by converting activities, processes and effective presentations  that has the power to turn any potential client in to a loyal customer.</p>
			                            </figcaption>           
			                        </figure>
			                        <figure class="effect-slideup one-forth">
			                            <img src="/wt_office_hunddle/static/src/images/7marketing.png" alt="img02"/>
			                            <figcaption class="gray">
			                                <p>Create a system that delivers your products and services efficiently by understanding product design, production, delivery subsystem, and customer service.</p>
			                            </figcaption>           
			                        </figure> 
			                    </div>
			                </div>
			            </div>
